flowchart TD
    subgraph Orchestrator["Orchestrator (Main Claude)"]
        Start[タスク開始] --> WF_Start[workflow_start]
        WF_Start --> GetPhase[現在フェーズ取得]
        GetPhase --> CheckPhaseType{フェーズタイプ?}

        CheckPhaseType -->|単一| SinglePhase
        CheckPhaseType -->|並列| ParallelPhase
        CheckPhaseType -->|完了| End[タスク完了]

        subgraph SinglePhase["単一フェーズ実行"]
            S1[プロンプト準備] --> S2[Task tool呼び出し]
            S2 --> S3[結果待機]
            S3 --> S4{成功?}
            S4 -->|Yes| S5[workflow_next]
            S4 -->|No| S6[エラー処理]
            S6 --> S7{再実行?}
            S7 -->|Yes| S1
            S7 -->|No| ErrorEnd[中断]
        end

        subgraph ParallelPhase["並列フェーズ実行"]
            P1[サブフェーズ特定] --> P2[複数Task同時起動]
            P2 --> P3[全結果待機]
            P3 --> P4{全成功?}
            P4 -->|Yes| P5[workflow_complete_sub x N]
            P5 --> P6[workflow_next]
            P4 -->|No| P7[失敗サブフェーズ特定]
            P7 --> P8{再実行?}
            P8 -->|Yes| P2
            P8 -->|No| ErrorEnd
        end

        S5 --> GetPhase
        P6 --> GetPhase
    end

    subgraph Subagent["subagent"]
        SA1[起動] --> SA2[入力ファイル読み込み]
        SA2 --> SA3[フェーズ作業実行]
        SA3 --> SA4[成果物書き出し]
        SA4 --> SA5[結果返却]
    end

    S2 -.->|起動| SA1
    SA5 -.->|結果| S3
